                <p>Hero MotoCorp, India’s largest two-wheeler manufacturer, has unveiled the latest iteration of its iconic Karizma XMR 210 at the EICMA 2024 in Milan, Italy. The Karizma XMR 210 boasts an evolved design and enhanced performance features, underscoring Hero's renewed focus on the premium motorcycle segment. This version of the Karizma brings Hero’s legendary brand to a new generation of riders with sporty aesthetics and advanced mechanics.</p>
                <div class="row m-b20">
